    <note>Zhang(1) Ruogu [245] Kui(3)'s father, Jin [202] and Jing [203] have the same generational name as his grandsons. His career was assisted by Zhang(1) Shixun [279]. Gong(2) Yuan's [941] grandfather-in-law. Kui(3) [3150] was Wang(2) Yi(3)'s [7082] son-in-law. Jiangxi TZ, 9.14a; XCB, 61.12b, 13a, 73.20a, 101.11a-11b, 104.19b, 109.4b; SS, 299.4b; Wang(2) Anshi, WJ, 99.1021; Wu Tingxie, BeiSong jingfu nianbao, p. 114; Fujian TZ, 147.4b. CBD, 3, 2395.</note>
